            the Additional Warranties.
          </p>
          <h5>8.2. From Customer.</h5>
          <p class="mb-6 text-sm">
            Customer represents and warrants that it, all Users, and anyone
            submitting Customer Content each have and will continue to have all
            rights necessary to submit or make available Customer Content to the
