          </p>
          <h5>8.4. Provider Warranty Remedy.</h5>
          <p class="mb-6 text-sm">
            If Provider breaches the warranty in Section 8.4 (Provider Warranty
            Remedy), Customer must give Provider notice (with enough detail for
            Provider to understand or replicate the issue) within 45 days of
