          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="limitation-liability" class="scroll-mt-4">
        <h4>10. Limitation of Liability</h4>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h5>10.1. Liability Caps</h5>
          <p class="mb-6 text-sm">
            Except as provided in Section 10.4 (Exceptions), each party’s total
            cumulative liability for all claims arising out of or relating to
            this Agreement will not exceed the amounts paid or payable by
            Customer to Provider under this Agreement during the twelve (12)
