            liability arising out of or relating to this Agreement will not
            exceed two (2) times the General Cap (the "Increased Cap").
          </p>
          <h5>10.2. Damages Waiver.</h5>
          <p class="mb-6 text-sm">
            Except as provided in Section 10.4 (Exceptions), under no
            circumstances will either party be liable to the other for lost
            profits or revenues (whether direct or indirect), or for
            consequential, special, indirect, exemplary, punitive, or incidental
